<P>April 11          <B>Dinesh D'Souza </B>at the University of Iowa
<P>April 12-13     <B>California Leadership Conference 
</B>at the Atrium Hotel in Irvine, California; featuring <B>Walter 
Williams</B>, <B>Oliver North</B>, <B>Dinesh D'Souza</B>, Judge <B>William 
Clark</B>, and <B>Armstrong Williams</B>
<P>April 18          <B>William F. Buckley </B>at Weber State University
<P>April 24          <B>Jack Kemp </B>at Loyola University-Chicago
<P>April 30          <B>Clarence Thomas </B>at Southeast Missouri State University
<P>May 6          <B>Michael Medved </B>at Union College
