<html><head><title>Campus Leader Volume 4, Issue 5</title><center><img src="cl-logo.gif"><h4>A Newsletter For Student Leaders From Young America's Foundation</h4>Volume 4, Number 5<br>
<hr><p>
<a name="contents"><h3>Contents</h3></a>
<a href="#speakers">'95 Speakers Booklet Includes Buckley, Reed,D'Souza, and Quayle</a><br>
<a href="#gov">Is the Government Crushing Your Job Prospects?</a><br>
