<h2>James B. Taylor</h2>
<table align=left width="200" hspace="5">
<tr><td><img alt="Picture of James Taylor" src="taylor.gif">
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p>James B. Taylor is executive director of Young America's Foundation.  He was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania and is a graduate of Swarthmore College.
<P>
 Before coming to Young America's Foundation Mr. Taylor was eastern director of the Intercollegiate Studies Institute, public relations director for the National Right to Work Legal Defense Foundation, and assistant to the president of the Freedoms Foundation at Valley Forge.
<P>
 Mr. Taylor is an authority on the American campus; his articles have appeared in the <I>Wall Street Journal, </I>the <I>Washington Times, Insight Magazine, </I>and the <I>Lincoln Review.</I><p><p>
