http://www.savers.org:80/heritage/dept_writeups/95lect.html 204.71.237.73 19970108032851 text/html 2942
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 03:29:07 GMT
