<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><CENTER><B>Discovery Institute for Public Policy</B></CENTER>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<H1><CENTER>Mission Statement</CENTER>
</H1>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<H3><CENTER>Discovery Institute examines the past and explores the future
to develop public policies with transforming results now.<BR>
<HR WIDTH="27%"></CENTER>
</H3>
<B>Contemporary public policy is too reactive, often unconnected either
to conscious principles that have served civilization in the past or to
a sound understanding of the future. Discovery Institute was established
in 1990 to devise initiatives in regional, national and international affairs
that reflect a long term perspective and can better shape immediate decisions
in the public, profit, and voluntary sectors of society.<BR>
<P><CENTER></B><IMG SRC="blueball.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="BOTTOM"
NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><B><TT><A HREF="mission.html">How Discovery functions</A></TT></B></CENTER>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
