<h2>February's Contents</h2>
<b>2/29/96</b>
<ul>
<li><a href="/pff/bigchange/vlah0228.html">"The Meaning of Revolution,"</a> by Micahel Vlahos, of the Progress &amp; Freedom Foundation.
<li>The House of Representatives will soon vote on a bill to create a <a href="/townhall/FRC/radio/c96b29.html">National Commission on
     Gambling</a>. Find out more in FRC's radio commentary. 
<li>Empower America's <a href="/empower/cndschl.html">1996 Candidate Shool</a> will be devoted entirely to the issues, bringing together the
     best thinkers, ideas, and materials to help each candidate form a solid base of
     information and craft a winning message. 
<li>From the Heritage Foundation:
<ul>
