<li>Senators John Chafee and Arlen Specter have refused to vote to end the Democratic <a href="/conservative/lout0228.html">filibuster of the Dictrict of Columbia's approprations bill</a>. Find out more in ACU's <i>Latest Republican Outrage</i>.
<li>Phylis Schlafly comments on the games and tricks of <a href="/townhall/columnists/schl0222.html">the New World Order</a>.
<li>Wesley Pruden of <i>The Washington Times</i> relays a story and is sure to <a href="/wash_times/pruden.2-26.html">curdle the cream in Clinton's coffee</a>.
<li>From William F. Buckley:
<ul>
