<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-chavez.html.cgi/textonly">[Text View]</a></h5>

<center>
<h2>Linda Chavez</h2>
</center>


<p>


<img align="left" alt="Photo of Linda Chavez" 
hspace=8 vspace=25 src="/townhall/columnists/chavez.jpg">


<a href="/townhall/columnists/chavez.html"><b>Biography</b></a>
