<li>October 30, 1996 <a href="/townhall/columnists/chavez/chav103096.html">The clueless voter ought to stay home</a>
<li>October 25, 1996 <a href="/townhall/columnists/chavez/chav102596.html">Belgian outrage, our silence</a>
