<html>

<head>
<title>Columnist Llewellyn H. Rockwell</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>

<img src="/townhall/columnists/colm.gif">






</center>





<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-rockwell.html.cgi/textonly">[Text View]</a></h5>

<center>
<h2>Llewellyn H. Rockwell</h2>
</center>


<p>


<img align="left" alt="Photo of Llewellyn H. Rockwell" 
hspace=8 vspace=25 src="/townhall/columnists/rockwell.jpg">


